          Download Youtube video, list of videos, playlist Ubuntu Linux


install youtube-dl
command :sudo apt-get install youtube-dl



Download  a video :
copy the link ,open terminal ,command : youtube-dl [link]



Download selected multiple videos :
create a txt file and coppy the link of the videos .thn command :youtube-dl -a [txt file name]


Download from ith to jth of a  playlist:
command:youtube-dl --playlist-start=i --playlist-end=j [link]

Download full playlist:
command:youtube-dl [playlistlink]

Download video with substitle :
command:youtube-dl --write-auto-sub [link]




